detectors.description:
Contest.distributePrizes() () sends eth to arbitrary user
	Dangerous calls:
	- prizeOwner != 0 && ! owner.send(totalPrize / 10000 * prizeOwner) ()
	- prizeWinners[i] != 0 && ! winners[i].send(totalPrize / 10000 * prizeWinners[i]) ()
	- ! luckyVoters[j].send(amount) ()
	- ! owner.send(this.balance) ()
detectors.markdown:
[Contest.distributePrizes()]() sends eth to arbitrary user
	Dangerous calls:
	- [prizeOwner != 0 && ! owner.send(totalPrize / 10000 * prizeOwner)]()
	- [prizeWinners[i] != 0 && ! winners[i].send(totalPrize / 10000 * prizeWinners[i])]()
	- [! luckyVoters[j].send(amount)]()
	- [! owner.send(this.balance)]()

detectors.description:

	External calls:
	- distributePrizes() ()

		- prizeOwner != 0 && ! owner.send(totalPrize / 10000 * prizeOwner) ()
		- prizeReferee != 0 && ! referee.send(totalPrize / 10000 * prizeReferee) ()
		- prizeWinners[i] != 0 && ! winners[i].send(totalPrize / 10000 * prizeWinners[i]) ()
		- ! luckyVoters[j].send(amount) ()
		- ! owner.send(this.balance) ()
	Event emitted after the call(s):
	- ContestClosed(totalPrize,winners,luckyVoters) ()
detectors.markdown:
Reentrancy in [Contest.close()]():
	External calls:
	- [distributePrizes()]()
		- [! c4c.send(this.balance / 10000 * c4cfee)]()
		- [prizeOwner != 0 && ! owner.send(totalPrize / 10000 * prizeOwner)]()
		- [prizeReferee != 0 && ! referee.send(totalPrize / 10000 * prizeReferee)]()
		- [prizeWinners[i] != 0 && ! winners[i].send(totalPrize / 10000 * prizeWinners[i])]()
		- [! luckyVoters[j].send(amount)]()
		- [! owner.send(this.balance)]()
